description: Israeli prime minister Benjamin Netanyahu called the killing of a Israeli-Moldovan rabbi in the United Arab Emirates an 'antisemitic terrorist attack' after the 28-year-old's body was found. Authorities in the UAE have arrested three individuals in connection to the murder of Kogan, who ran a Kosher shop in Dubai.
title: Netanyahu condemns the killing of rabbi as an 'antisemitic terrorist attack'

description: Government officials met with tribal leaders in northwestern Pakistan on Sunday to try to mediate a ceasefire between rival sectarian groups after days of clashes that have killed at least 68 people and injured dozens.
title: Pakistan government mediators seek ceasefire as 68 killed in sectarian violence

description: A gunman was dead and three policemen injured after a shooting near the Israeli embassy in neighbouring Jordan, a security source and state media said Sunday.
title: Gunman shot dead, 3 police injured in shooting near Israeli embassy in Jordan

description: LAS VEGAS — Max Verstappen clinched his fourth Formula 1 world championship Saturday night under the bright lights of Sin City, cementing his standing among the legends of the sport.
title: Max Verstappen clinches fourth Formula 1 world championship in Las Vegas
